	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just came up with another solution.  For my future SNES games, I'll implement variable slot height into my self-defragmenting variable sized slot dynamic animation engine.  So far, only variable width have been implemented.  This means I can have a 32x40 sprite stored in ROM without compressing it to fit within 64x16, without wasting too much extra room.

		

		</td>
